/*This program takes a bunch of inputs and maps them as a game controller in windows. It has 16 buttons, 1 8-way hat switch in the form of 2 on/off/on switches, 5 analog levers in the form of motors, and 6 rotary encoders.

/////////////////////////////to do list/////////////////////////////
assemble motors
assemble push buttons
assemble button matrix
assemble hat switch
design and assemble box

/////////////////////////////github links to libraries for furutre reference/////////////////////////////

https://github.com/mheironimus/arduinojoysticklibrary
https://github.com/Chris--A/Keypad/blob/master/examples/CustomKeypad/CustomKeypad.ino
